06daba80b27a9aec46c3c4331a353725e7cb6beb.query:
UPDATE
                    tasks
                SET
                    completed_at = CASE
                        WHEN $2 THEN CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'UTC'
                        ELSE NULL
                    END
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    completed_at

0a38a4263db5e25680c5a7280cc1405c5af305f3.query:
DELETE FROM
                    tasks
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId"

0d135aab26cdee63c92e2bba0380efbec22a1164.query:
SELECT
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at
                FROM
                    tasks

155da0c5a5aeed9f52f42b50c1a2b48ba484dcbe.query:
UPDATE
                    tasks
                SET
                    title = $2
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at

312c98c98346c19d40e8c3bfcd87ec1ba305596d.query:
INSERT INTO tasks (
                    title
                )
                VALUES (
                    $1
                )
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at
